snippet.title: Rat it - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Watch the latest trailer for Rat It to see gameplay from this single-player magic shooter as you take down rats and evil monsters on a medieval sailing ship. Wield your powerful slingshot and get ready for a new chapter of Rat It in 2024, coming to Meta Quest and Steam.
